      {
        "idx": 2,
        "description": "x>3：g(x)=∫0^3(t+1)dt + ∫3^x(-2t+10)dt = 15/2 + [(-t^2+10t)]_3^x = -x^2+10x-27/2。",
        "math": "g(x)=-x^2+10x-\\frac{27}{2}"
